                     <p>The manuscript is written in <origPlace>Denmark</origPlace>. <name type="person" key="KriKaa001">Kristian Kålund</name> (<bibl>
                           <ref type="secondary" target="KKKat">Katalog</ref>
                           <biblScope type="volume">I</biblScope>
                           <biblScope type="pages">340</biblScope>
                        </bibl>) has dated it to c. 1500, whereas <name type="person" key="PetSka001">Peter
                    Skautrup</name> (<bibl>
                           <ref type="primary-2" target="DGL2">Danmarks gamle Landskabslove</ref>
                           <biblScope type="volume">II</biblScope>
                           <biblScope type="pages">xvi</biblScope>
                        </bibl>) has dated it to <origDate>the end of the fifteenth century</origDate>.</p>
